headline: If I Could Buy Only 1 Warren Buffett Stock Over the Next 10 Years, Pool Corp. Would Be It. Here's the Key Reason.
summary: Warren Buffett is not known for buying the most exciting businesses out there, but he is known for making some of the best investments.  Remember that, even if new pool construction growth is slowing, the installed base of pools is still growing, creating opportunities for Pool Corp.
